---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About Us">
  <div class="bg-blue-200">
    <div class="py-30 flex flex-col justify-center px-5 text-center md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 m-auto">
      <p class="text-3xl font-semibold">Welcome to Our Directory! üìç</p>
      <div class="h-5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="text-lg">
        <p class="pb-5">I'm Alex, the creator behind this directory website. Like you, I'm always looking for great local businesses and services when I'm out exploring.</p>
        <p class="pb-5">I enjoy discovering new places and sharing them with friends and family. There's nothing better than finding a hidden gem in your neighborhood or while traveling.</p>
        <p class="pb-5">Recently, I found myself in an unfamiliar neighborhood with friends and we were looking for a place to visit. After spending way too long scrolling online and looking through unhelpful information, we finally found something decent ‚Äì but the whole experience got me thinking.</p>
        <p class="pb-5">Why wasn't there a better resource for people to find quality local businesses? A place where we could easily find what we're looking for anywhere we go? And so, this website was born.</p>
        <p class="pb-5">My mission is simple: help people find great local businesses without the hassle. No more settling for mediocre options when there's an amazing spot just around the corner you didn't know about.</p>
        <p class="pb-5">This site is constantly evolving and I will keep adding more to it so that it covers every possible region in the future!</p>
        <p class="pb-5">Thanks for stopping by, and happy exploring!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>